data.description: Take a look at this Flour Bluff ISD beauty that has been updated and very well maintained. Located near shopping, grocery stores, NAS/CCAD, South Padre Island Drive, the beach, boat launches and walking and an short walk to Retta park. This home features 3 bedrooms, two baths, two car garage, large yard with sprinklers a covered back porch for family and friends to gather (storage building included). Inside you will find split bedrooms, an updated stand- up shower in the primary suite, wood laminate floors, quartz kitchen counter tops, stainless steel appliances (including refrigerator), updated fixtures and a woodburning fireplace in the vaulted living room.
